ananda. He asked whether the siddhis will enable him to realize god. Ramakr=
ishna said no. Vivekananda firmly declined the offer then! Of course, when =
Ramakrishna gave them anyway later, he accepted them. Vivekananda's two act=
ions demonstrate Vasishtha's instructions well.</FONT></DIV>
