</DIV>
<DIV align=3Dleft><FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana>Ther=
e are some trees that are found at lower altitudes also, but some really sp=
ecial trees are found at very high altitudes only. If one has such a fruit,=
 it shows that one has climbed great heights. Similarly, some siddhis do no=
t mean much, but some siddhis are very special and only really elevated sad=
hakas can obtain them (whether by trying or without trying). If a sadhakas =
demonstrates such a siddhi, you can see that one progressed a lot. However,=
 the key is that one who climbed the same or more distance may not have tha=
t or any other fruit. </FONT></DIV>
